text: Jack Majgaard Jensen (born 25 March 1973 is a Danish football manager who currently manages Vålerenga Fotball Damer in Toppserien. He has previously managed Lunds BK, Lyngby BK, FC Rosengård (women), and Landskrona BoIS. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Danish football managers Category:Landskrona BoIS managers Category:Lunds BK managers
